---
import '../styles/tailwind.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Portfolio</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="relative isolate flex min-h-screen flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10 backdrop-aurora">
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-[-14%] h-[30rem] w-[30rem] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-aurora-royal/45 blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute right-[6%] top-[20%] h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-aurora-sky/35 blur-[130px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-[-18%] left-[12%] h-[28rem] w-[28rem] rounded-full bg-aurora-ember/35 blur-[140px]"></div>
      </div>

      <section class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl space-y-14 rounded-[46px] border border-white/25 bg-white/80 p-10 shadow-glow backdrop-blur-2xl md:p-16">
        <header class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-center md:text-left">
          <span class="mx-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 self-start rounded-full border border-aurora-midnight/10 bg-aurora-dawn/70 px-5 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-aurora-midnight shadow-pill md:mx-0">
            Tema Aurora 4
          </span>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h1 class="text-balance text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.05] text-aurora-midnight sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
              Diseña historias visuales con personalidad
            </h1>
            <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-pretty text-base leading-relaxed text-aurora-midnight/80 md:text-lg">
              Un portafolio elegante alimentado por Tailwind CSS v4, inspirado en luces del norte y destellos cálidos. Conecta tus proyectos con una narrativa visual fresca, tipografías contrastantes y detalles brillantes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 md:justify-start">
          <a
            class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-aurora-royal px-8 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-aurora-dawn shadow-pill transition duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-aurora-midnight"
            href="https://docs.astro.build/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            Explorar Astro
            <span aria-hidden="true" class="transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
          </a>
          <a
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-aurora-midnight/15 px-8 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-aurora-midnight transition duration-200 hover:border-aurora-midnight/40 hover:text-aurora-royal"
            href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            Guía de Tailwind 4
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.3fr,0.7fr]">
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
              <article class="flex flex-col gap-3 rounded-3xl border border-aurora-midnight/10 bg-white/75 p-6 shadow-sm">
                <span class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-aurora-sky/40 shadow-inner"></span>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-aurora-midnight">Paleta inmersiva</h2>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-aurora-midnight/70">
                  Combina tonos atlánticos y acentos bronce para un ambiente sofisticado que destaca proyectos creativos.
                </p>
              </article>
              <article class="flex flex-col gap-3 rounded-3xl border border-aurora-midnight/10 bg-white/75 p-6 shadow-sm">
                <span class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-aurora-royal/45 shadow-inner"></span>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-aurora-midnight">Componentes expresivos</h2>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-aurora-midnight/70">
                  Botones suaves, sombras difusas y fondos translúcidos generan una experiencia limpia y moderna.
                </p>
              </article>
              <article class="flex flex-col gap-3 rounded-3xl border border-aurora-midnight/10 bg-white/75 p-6 shadow-sm">
                <span class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-aurora-ember/40 shadow-inner"></span>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-aurora-midnight">Animada por Tailwind 4</h2>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-aurora-midnight/70">
                  Utiliza la nueva generación de utilidades para iterar más rápido, con tokens y layouts listos para personalizar.
                </p>
              </article>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-3xl border border-aurora-midnight/10 bg-white/75 p-8 shadow-sm">
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-aurora-midnight">Paleta Aurora</h2>
                <p class="text-sm text-aurora-midnight/70">Ordenada para equilibrar profundidad, brillo y calidez.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-5">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-center">
                  <span class="h-16 w-full rounded-2xl bg-aurora-midnight"></span>
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-aurora-midnight/80">Midnight</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-aurora-midnight/60">#575373</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-center">
                  <span class="h-16 w-full rounded-2xl bg-aurora-royal"></span>
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-aurora-midnight/80">Royal</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-aurora-midnight/60">#3B478C</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-center">
                  <span class="h-16 w-full rounded-2xl bg-aurora-sky"></span>
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-aurora-midnight/80">Sky</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-aurora-midnight/60">#6698D9</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-center">
                  <span class="h-16 w-full rounded-2xl bg-aurora-dawn"></span>
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-aurora-midnight/80">Dawn</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-aurora-midnight/60">#F2DDB6</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-center">
                  <span class="h-16 w-full rounded-2xl bg-aurora-ember"></span>
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-aurora-midnight/80">Ember</span>
                  <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-aurora-midnight/60">#A67A46</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <aside class="flex h-full flex-col gap-8 rounded-3xl bg-aurora-midnight/95 p-8 text-aurora-dawn shadow-[0_45px_90px_-45px_rgba(59,71,140,0.65)] sm:p-10">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-aurora-dawn">Tipografías con carácter</h2>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-aurora-dawn/80">
                Playfair Display aporta un toque editorial a los encabezados, mientras que Manrope garantiza lectura pulida en párrafos y llamadas a la acción.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/10 p-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-aurora-dawn/80">
              <p class="font-display text-xl text-white">Playfair Display</p>
              <p class="mt-2 font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-aurora-dawn/70">Manrope Regular</p>
              <p class="mt-4">
                Ajusta pesos y tamaños con utilidades de Tailwind 4 para lograr jerarquías dinámicas y consistentes.
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-aurora-dawn/60">Listo para personalizar</p>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
